{"tid":2083192,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"天水圍朋友小心啲","createTime":"2020-06-28T14:40:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-28T16:44:44.000Z","uid":308006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ea6ed943e9b90f306a7ef6c99f062d5af4fe1889","tid":2083192,"uid":308006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T14:40:28.000Z","msg":"天一商場拜x庭有個part time 借鋪頭名黎呃人 要去到舖頭門口同個老細講 個老細先啱啱知道發生咩事<br />\n話說條友用公司名水人買貨 有話咩最後優惠 到頭黎件貨由原本第二日交收 拖左<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">七日</span></span>都未收到 keep住話咩運輸問題 另一個苦主仲要被條友玩足<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">1個月</span></span> <br />\n黃店個朵都俾佢整臭埋 淨係叫佢退錢都要三催四請 仲夠膽話冇銀行戶口 要用咩Tap &amp; Go等兩日去過數 真係屌撚咗出聲<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/em3T5N1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fem3T5N1.jpg&h=6e2267e4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5xVrGmm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5xVrGmm.jpg&h=7590ea76&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Tt9v71n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTt9v71n.jpg&h=f8478d30&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qGAvozJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqGAvozJ.png&h=dfd0d2ba&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1tQnY74.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1tQnY74.png&h=cf1df955&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9e9b507fb737b0b988dfce55928af467a5b44807","tid":2083192,"uid":172999,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T14:44:37.000Z","msg":"有無詳細啲 <br />\n天水圍人都唔知咩事"},{"pid":"ce80726742b192c1dcf3401ae5dbbc0eba4db03b","tid":2083192,"uid":308006,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"9e9b507fb737b0b988dfce55928af467a5b44807","tid":2083192,"uid":172999,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T14:44:37.000Z","msg":"有無詳細啲 <br />\n天水圍人都唔知咩事"},"cit